last
time.
It
feels
weird.
But
remember,
you're
not
unemployed
now
�
you�re
self-employed.
You
are
now
at
a
turning
point
in
your
life.
You
might
never
have
to
commute
into
work
again.
You
may
be
able
to
do
whatever
you
want
from
now
on,
both
