that
rely
entirely
on
personal
referrals
for
their
business,
and
only
maintain
social
network
profiles
to
market
themselves.
If
you
can
get
by
without
a
website,
then
that's
a
lot
of
expense
and
maintenance
you
can
avoid.
You
are
giving
up
some
potential
marketing
channels,
however,
if
