to
your
industry?
Can
you
guest-blog
on
a
popular
website
your
customers
frequent?
There
are
many
creative
ways
to
get
your
name�
and
your
company's
name�
out
there.
BASICS
OF
ONLINE
ADVERTISING
Online
advertising
is
paid
efforts
to
drive
new
customers
to
your
