BEWARE
OF
HIRING
SALESPEOPLE
I've
already
given
you
my
horror
story
on
sales
people
above,
but
it's
one
I've
heard
repeatedly
from
others�
including
from
career
sales
people!
I
was
fortunate
that
all
I
lost
was
some
time
with
my
experiment
in
sales.
However,
the
