person
I
worked
with
originally
wanted
a
share
of
the
company
in
exchange
for
his
efforts.
Had
I
agreed,
I�d
be
burdened
with
that
drain
on
my
company
with
nothing
in
exchange.
Despite
how
comfortable
or
not
you
are
with
sales,
the
