your
company's
reputation.
Within
a
small
niche,
that
reputation
can
spread
quickly.
The
only
person
who
really
has
the
depth
required
to
answer
technical
questions
from
your
customers
is
probably
you;
other
people
may
be
useful
in
identifying
leads,
but
you�re
the
best
person
to
actually
talk
to
them.
If
