because
you
were
too
busy?
How
many
unique
experiences
does
your
area
have
to
offer?
Have
you
ever
had
time
to
travel
just
for
pleasure?
Have
you
ever
considered
moving
just
for
the
opportunity
to
intimately
experience
someplace
new
and
interesting?
While
you
had
a
job,
your
money
was
probably
spent
mostly
on
things,
because
you
didn't
have
time
to
